        """Resolve options whose ``default`` is a dynamic default mapping.

        Runs after every parameter has been parsed, so it can use the
        final values of the options it depends on. Only applies to
        options whose value came from :attr:`ParameterSource.DEFAULT`,
        i.e. no value was given on the command line, in an environment
        variable, or in ``default_map``.
